        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-[#fcfaf6] mb-4 leading-tight">高雄居家看護的日常：一位家屬從摸索到安心的過程</h1>
        <div class="flex items-center text-[#efe5d5] text-sm space-x-4">
          <span>2025-01-22</span><span>12 分鐘閱讀</span>
        </div>
